'''''Mah-e Asal''''' ({{lang-fa|ماه عسل}}, meaning [[Honeymoon]]) is an [[Iran|Iranian]], [[Persian language]], popular daily television program broadcast by [[Channel 3 (Iran)|Channel 3]] during [[Ramadan]]. The host of the program is [[Ehsan Alikhani]]. The main subject of the program is the life of people who have had an extraordinary rare experience.<ref>{{cite web |title=ماجرای بیماری ناشناخته مهمان «ماه عسل» |url=https://www.mashreghnews.ir/news/860309 |website=[[Mashregh News]] |accessdate=31 May 2018 |language=fa |date=30 May 2018}}</ref>
