{{Infobox government agency |agency_name = National Institute of Civil Aviation of Portugal |type = |nativename = Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I. P. |nativename_a = |nativename_r = |logo = |logo_width = |logo_caption = |seal = |seal_width = |seal_caption = |picture = |picture_width = |picture_caption = |formed = {{Start date|2007|4|27|df=y}} |preceding1 = Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil |preceding2 = <!-- (etc.) --> |dissolved = |superseding = |jurisdiction = [[Government of Portugal]] |headquarters = [[Lisbon Portela Airport]] |coordinates = {{coord|38|46|53|N|9|8|10|W|type:landmark|display=inline}} |employees = |budget = |minister1_name = |minister1_pfo = |minister2_name = |minister2_pfo = <!-- (etc.) --> |deputyminister1_name = |deputyminister1_pfo = |deputyminister2_name = |deputyminister2_pfo = <!-- (etc.) --> |chief1_name = Luís Miguel Pereira Trindade Santos |chief1_position = [[Managing Director]] |agency_type = |parent_department = |parent_agency = |child1_agency = |child2_agency = <!-- (etc.) --> |keydocument1 = <!-- (etc.) --> |website = {{URL|www.inac.pt}} |footnotes = Sources: INAC, I.P.,<ref name="Our History">{{cite web|title= A nossa História|language= Portuguese|trans-title=Our history|url= http://www.inac.pt/vPT/Generico/INAC/QuemSomos/Historia/Paginas/Historia.aspx|work= Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I.P.|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/66RKPS2e2|archivedate= {{date|2012-3-26}}|accessdate= {{date|2012-3-26}}}}</ref><ref name="Contact Us">{{cite web|title= Contacte-nos|language= Portuguese|trans-title=Contact Us|url= http://www.inac.pt/vPT/Generico/Contactos/Paginas/Contactos.aspx|work= Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I.P.|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/66RKX9eDE|archivedate= {{date|2012-3-26}}|accessdate= {{date|2012-3-26}}}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title= Conselho Directivo|language= Portuguese|trans-title=Directorate Council|url= http://www.inac.pt/vPT/Generico/INAC/OrganizacaoEstrutura/ConselhoDirectivo/Paginas/ConselhoDirectivo.aspx|work= Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I.P.|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/66RKfE9KQ|archivedate= {{date|2012-3-26}}|accessdate= {{date|2012-3-26}}}}</ref> World Aero Data<ref>{{WAD|LPPT|Lisbon Portela Airport}}</ref> |map = |map_width = |map_caption = }} The '''National Institute of Civil Aviation of Portugal''' ({{lang-pt|'''Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I.P.'''}}), often shortened to ''ANAC, I.P.'', is the [[civil aviation authority]] of [[Portugal]]. It oversees all aspects of civil aviation within the [[Portugal|Portuguese]] territory and all its dependencies.<ref>{{cite web|title= Missão, Visão e Valores|language= Portuguese|trans-title=Mission, Vision, and Worthiness|url= http://www.inac.pt/vPT/Generico/INAC/QuemSomos/Missao/Paginas/MissaoValores.aspx|work= Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I.P.|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/66RKkpkEq|archivedate= {{date|2012-3-26}}|accessdate= {{date|2012-3-26}}}}</ref>
The ''ANAC, I.P.'' was created on {{date|2007-4-27}} to succeed the former ''National Institute of Civil Aviation ''&nbsp;({{lang-pt|Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil}}), which had been created on {{date|1998-5-15}} for taking over the ''General Directorate of Civil Aviation''&nbsp;({{lang-pt|Direcção-Geral da Aviação Civil}}).<ref name="Our History"/>
The body is organised into a Directorate Council -which is in turn sub-divided into five Directorates and three Cabinets-, a Consultant Council, and a Finance Council.<ref>{{cite web|title= Organograma|language= Portuguese|trans-title=Organisational chart|url= http://www.inac.pt/vPT/Generico/INAC/OrganizacaoEstrutura/Organograma/Paginas/Organograma.aspx|work= Instituto Nacional de Aviação Civil, I.P.|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/66RKpt0N1|archivedate= {{date|2012-3-26}}|accessdate= {{date|2012-3-26}}}}</ref> It has its headquarters in [[Lisbon Portela Airport]].<ref name="Contact Us"/>
